Comments:
This is a prefab which with it we can play payload on CSS ! 

The Payload:
The Payload can be only pushed by CT's (blue for me) but you can change it with the team filtrer include in it.

How to install it?:
Well is quite easy, unzip the file with a software who can open .rar file, then open the .vmf file with hammer. Then copy everything in it into your map. Then continue the track.

Need help or a bug?:
You can ask me in feedback ! I'll try to help you but I do not promise you that I can solve everything !

You have an suggestion?:
So feedback me ! It will help me a lot in improving my "mod"

One last word:
Don't forget to credit me if you're using my prefab!

I hope you will enjoy my work !
